#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/liquibase.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Inject the Quarkus liquibase factory if you want to use the liquibase methods directly"
msgstr "如果想直接使用 Liquibase 方法，请注入 Quarkus Liquibase 工厂"

